---
title: Turkey & Figgy Apple Picnic Sandos with Creamy Honey Mustard, Carrot Sticks & Hummus Dipper
description: Heading for a hike, the park, the beach? We’ve got your picnic plan right here, and it’s perfectly portable! Chewy toasted ciabatta is spread with creamy honey mustard sauce and fig jam, then layered with a complementary duo of juicy turkey and crisp apple slices. Wrap ’em up pro-stye, serve with crunchy carrots and hummus, and you’re ready for anything!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/665df8c307c68e1e8bb69c43-2b586908.jpeg
